heke
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:one who migrates, party of emigrants, migration, a migration, a body of migrating or travelling people,  cf hikoi.
Origin: Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
